August 10th, 2020 X-Wing Vassal news

NEW: Events (leagues and tournaments for Vassal X-Wing) here: https://tinyurl.com/tgdo3gp (Google Calendar)
Module website is at: http://xwvassal.info
Tutorial guide for this module: http://xwvassal.info/guide

New v9.0.0 X-Wing module is out. Match it with the latest Vassal client software v3.3.2 from http://vassalengine.org

The Unofficial X-Wing Vassal League home website (season 10 is ending soon): https://listfortress.com/league

Windows players: ctrl-left-click on ships (while they are on the map) to access the ship mouse interface (new feature in 2019)
Mac players: rightmost option-left-click on ships

